# Cloudflare Pages clean-URL routing.
# /privacy → /privacy.html, etc. The 200 status (not 301) means the
# browser address bar keeps the clean URL while the server serves the
# .html. This matches the URLs already published in App Store Connect
# notes and avoids any visible .html in marketing references.
/privacy        /privacy.html        200
/accessibility  /accessibility.html  200
/support        /support.html        200
